She smiled at Prebon. "I hope it will work. I hope I was able to 
convince them." She took Prebon's arm and walked with him. "Master, 
may I go say good bye to Striker now. I just have the feelling 
that...well...for old time's sake."  She smiled and kissed Prebon's 
cheek, "No need to worry master Prebon.  I shall stay here, with you 
and serve you...always"
